reviewText: Loved it! got it for me and the Wife  to watch and see How To Give Each Other a better  massage and spice things up good Mood Setting
I bought this to help our sex life by giving us new ideas and reminding us of things we forgot.  It helped.

The best by far massage DVD that teaches the enjoyment and benefits of massage.

Very beautifully filmed. Outstanding music. Beautiful cast. Wonderful voice over.

You will be proud to share the benefits of The Magic of Massage with your

partner.
